<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>While I was installing ZF on a new server I noticed, that Zend_Cache_Backend::getTmpDir() returns document root instead of temp directory. The reason was that the server set $_SERVER['TMP'] as a false value and the code in getTmpDir() checks it only via isset(). I would therefore recommend checking also the value.</p>

